#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn54.1"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn54.1:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 54 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 54 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn54.1:0.2"
msgid "1. Ekadhammavagga "
msgstr "1. One Thing "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn54.1:0.3"
msgid "1. Ekadhammasutta "
msgstr "1. One Thing "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.311, sc1
msgctxt "sn54.1:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn54.1:1.2"
msgid "Tatra kho … pe … etadavoca: "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn54.1:1.3"
msgid "“ekadhammo, bhikkhave, bhāvito bahulīkato mahapphalo hoti mahānisaṃso. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, when one thing is developed and cultivated it’s very fruitful and beneficial. "

msgctxt "sn54.1:1.4"
msgid "Katamo ekadhammo? "
msgstr "What one thing? "

#. VAR: Ānāpānassati → ānāpānasati (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "sn54.1:1.5"
msgid "Ānāpānassati. "
msgstr "Mindfulness of breathing. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn54.1:1.6"
msgid "Kathaṃ bhāvitā ca, bhikkhave, ānāpānassati kathaṃ bahulīkatā mahapphalā hoti mahānisaṃsā? "
msgstr "And how is mindfulness of breathing developed and cultivated to be very fruitful and beneficial? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn54.1:1.7"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu araññagato vā rukkhamūlagato vā suññāgāragato vā nisīdati pallaṅkaṃ ābhujitvā ujuṃ kāyaṃ paṇidhāya parimukhaṃ satiṃ upaṭṭhapetvā. "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant has gone to a wilderness, or to the root of a tree, or to an empty hut. They sit down cross-legged, with their body straight, and establish mindfulness right there. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn54.1:1.8"
msgid "So satova assasati, satova passasati. "
msgstr "Just mindful, they breathe in. Mindful, they breathe out. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn54.1:2.1"
msgid "Dīghaṃ vā assasanto ‘dīghaṃ assasāmī’ti pajānāti, dīghaṃ vā passasanto ‘dīghaṃ passasāmī’ti pajānāti; "
msgstr "When breathing in heavily they know: ‘I’m breathing in heavily.’ When breathing out heavily they know: ‘I’m breathing out heavily.’ "

msgctxt "sn54.1:2.2"
msgid "rassaṃ vā assasanto ‘rassaṃ assasāmī’ti pajānāti, rassaṃ vā passasanto ‘rassaṃ passasāmī’ti pajānāti; "
msgstr "When breathing in lightly they know: ‘I’m breathing in lightly.’ When breathing out lightly they know: ‘I’m breathing out lightly.’ "

msgctxt "sn54.1:2.3"
msgid "‘sabbakāyappaṭisaṃvedī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘sabbakāyappaṭisaṃvedī passasissāmī’ti sikkhati; "
msgstr "They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe in experiencing the whole body.’ They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe out experiencing the whole body.’ "

msgctxt "sn54.1:2.4"
msgid "‘passambhayaṃ kāyasaṅkhāraṃ assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘passambhayaṃ kāyasaṅkhāraṃ passasissāmī’ti sikkhati. "
msgstr "They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe in stilling physical processes.’ They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe out stilling physical processes.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.312, sc3
msgctxt "sn54.1:3.1"
msgid "‘Pītippaṭisaṃvedī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘pītippaṭisaṃvedī passasissāmī’ti sikkhati; "
msgstr "They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe in experiencing rapture.’ They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe out experiencing rapture.’ "

msgctxt "sn54.1:3.2"
msgid "‘sukhappaṭisaṃvedī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘sukhappaṭisaṃvedī passasissāmī’ti sikkhati; "
msgstr "They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe in experiencing bliss.’ They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe out experiencing bliss.’ "

msgctxt "sn54.1:3.3"
msgid "‘cittasaṅkhārappaṭisaṃvedī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘cittasaṅkhārappaṭisaṃvedī passasissāmī’ti sikkhati; "
msgstr "They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe in experiencing mental processes.’ They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe out experiencing mental processes.’ "

msgctxt "sn54.1:3.4"
msgid "‘passambhayaṃ cittasaṅkhāraṃ assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘passambhayaṃ cittasaṅkhāraṃ passasissāmī’ti sikkhati. "
msgstr "They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe in stilling mental processes.’ They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe out stilling mental processes.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn54.1:4.1"
msgid "‘Cittappaṭisaṃvedī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘cittappaṭisaṃvedī passasissāmī’ti sikkhati; "
msgstr "They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe in experiencing the mind.’ They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe out experiencing the mind.’ "

msgctxt "sn54.1:4.2"
msgid "‘abhippamodayaṃ cittaṃ assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘abhippamodayaṃ cittaṃ passasissāmī’ti sikkhati; "
msgstr "They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe in gladdening the mind.’ They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe out gladdening the mind.’ "

msgctxt "sn54.1:4.3"
msgid "‘samādahaṃ cittaṃ assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘samādahaṃ cittaṃ passasissāmī’ti sikkhati; "
msgstr "They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe in immersing the mind in samādhi.’ They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe out immersing the mind in samādhi.’ "

msgctxt "sn54.1:4.4"
msgid "‘vimocayaṃ cittaṃ assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘vimocayaṃ cittaṃ passasissāmī’ti sikkhati; "
msgstr "They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe in freeing the mind.’ They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe out freeing the mind.’ "

msgctxt "sn54.1:4.5"
msgid "‘aniccānupassī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati. "
msgstr "They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe in observing impermanence.’ They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe out observing impermanence.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "sn54.1:5.1"
msgid "‘Aniccānupassī passasissāmī’ti sikkhati; "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn54.1:5.2"
msgid "‘virāgānupassī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘virāgānupassī passasissāmī’ti sikkhati; "
msgstr "They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe in observing fading away.’ They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe out observing fading away.’ "

msgctxt "sn54.1:5.3"
msgid "‘nirodhānupassī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘nirodhānupassī passasissāmī’ti sikkhati; "
msgstr "They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe in observing cessation.’ They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe out observing cessation.’ "

msgctxt "sn54.1:5.4"
msgid "‘paṭinissaggānupassī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘paṭinissaggānupassī passasissāmī’ti sikkhati. "
msgstr "They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe in observing letting go.’ They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe out observing letting go.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "sn54.1:6.1"
msgid "Evaṃ bhāvitā kho, bhikkhave, ānāpānassati evaṃ bahulīkatā mahapphalā hoti mahānisaṃsā”ti. "
msgstr "Mindfulness of breathing, when developed and cultivated in this way, is very fruitful and beneficial.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn54.1:6.2"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

